# qBittorrent (Material rewrite) — reusable QML components
#
# These types belong to the single application module `qBittorrent`
# (declared once via qt_add_qml_module in src/quick/CMakeLists.txt) and are
# therefore usable by name from any file in the module with no local import.
#
# This qmldir is an explicit inventory of the reusable component types living
# in this directory. There are NO singletons here — every entry is a plain,
# instantiable Material component. (The application singletons — Theme,
# Typography, Spacing, Icons, StateColors, I18n, Log, … — live elsewhere.)

